These Matlab scripts/functions represent an implementation of the transfer- and scattering-
matrix formalism described in "Intrinsically nonlocal metamaterials" manuscript by 
J. LaMountain et.al. To reproduce: 
- Transmission through metamaterial plots (Fig.6), run "transmissionFig.m"
- 2D dispersion plots (Fig.S5), run "nonlocalPCdispersion2D.m"
- 3D dispersion plots (Fig.S6) or field distribution plots (Fig.3), run "nonlocalPCdispersion3D_fields.m"
